fields.value: “I'm selfish, impatient and a little insecure. I make mistakes, I am out of control and at times hard to handle. But if you can't handle me at my worst, then you sure as hell don't deserve me at my best.”
fields.author: Marilyn Monroe

fields.value: “Be yourself; everyone else is already taken.”
fields.author: Oscar Wilde

fields.value: “Two things are infinite: the universe and human stupidity; and I'm not sure about the universe.”
fields.author: Albert Einstein

fields.value: “A room without books is like a body without a soul.”
fields.author: Marcus Tullius Cicero

fields.value: “Be who you are and say what you feel, because those who mind don't matter, and those who matter don't mind.”
fields.author: Bernard M. Baruch
